Save or Apply
The "Save" and "Apply" buttons should be available when configuring a new project.

Clicking "Save" should:
- Keep and store all project settings.
- Redirect the user to the project dashboard.

Clicking "Apply" should:
- Save changes without leaving the configuration page.
- Show a confirmation message that changes have been applied successfully.
Post-Build Actions
A "Post-Build Actions" section should be available during project setup.
The user should be able to add one or more post-build actions
